                  <div class="legend">
                    <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-swatch" style="background:#F84CA2;"></span><span>AI予測価格</span></div>
                    <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-swatch" style="background:#1ddcff;"></span><span>市場需給シグナル 78/100</span></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </section>

              <section class="panel">
                <div class="panel-head">
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="panel-title">DL意欲を押し上げる数字</h3>
                    <p class="panel-desc">ストアで理解できる指標だけを残した構成</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bars">
                  <div class="bar-row">
                    <div class="bar-label">個人情報不要</div>
                    <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill pink" style="--target:96%;"></div></div>
                    <div class="bar-value">96%</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bar-row">
                    <div class="bar-label">価格の即理解</div>
                    <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="--target:88%;"></div></div>
                    <div class="bar-value">88%</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bar-row">
                    <div class="bar-label">将来予測の新規性</div>
                    <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill pink" style="--target:92%;"></div></div>
                    <div class="bar-value">92%</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </section>

              <button class="cta">AIがあなたの愛車を査定</button>
              <div class="caption-foot">「価格だけ知りたい」に最短で答える1枚</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="device-column">
        <div class="device-header">
          <div>
            <div class="device-title">スクショB</div>
            <div class="device-subtitle">Android向け / 出費管理と将来予測を統合訴求</div>
          </div>
          <div class="device-badge">Android</div>
        </div>
        <div class="phone">
          <div class="screen" id="screen-b">
            <div class="status-bar">
              <span>9:41</span>
              <div class="notch"></div>
              <div class="status-icons"><span>Wi-Fi</span><span>100%</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="screen-inner">
              <section class="hero-card">
                <div class="chip-row">
                  <span class="chip">出費管理</span>
                  <span class="chip pink">将来予測</span>
                  <span class="chip">資産感覚で管理</span>
                </div>
                <p class="hero-title">維持費まで見えると、売り時判断が速くなる</p>
