                  <div class="mini-copy">相場下落と維持費の合算</div>
                </article>
              </div>

              <section class="panel">
                <div class="panel-head">
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="panel-title">価値と出費の推移</h3>
                    <p class="panel-desc">マネーアプリのように、車の価値を日常で見る</p>
                  </div>
                  <span class="panel-tag" id="b-signal">売り時 78</span>
                </div>
                <div class="chart-box">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 320 170" aria-label="価値と出費の推移グラフ">
                    <line class="grid-line" x1="24" y1="34" x2="296" y2="34"></line>
                    <line class="grid-line" x1="24" y1="86" x2="296" y2="86"></line>
