      </article>

      <article class="device-column">
        <div class="device-header">
          <div>
            <div class="device-title">スクショC</div>
            <div class="device-subtitle">競合比較 / 「電話0本」で負担を逆算させる</div>
          </div>
          <div class="device-badge">Compare</div>
        </div>
        <div class="phone">
          <div class="screen dark" id="screen-c">
            <div class="status-bar">
              <span>9:41</span>
              <div class="notch"></div>
              <div class="status-icons"><span>5G</span><span>100%</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="screen-inner">
              <section class="compare-card">
                <div class="compare-tabs">
                  <button class="compare-tab active" data-compare="estimate">相場確認時</button>
                  <button class="compare-tab" data-compare="contact">売却相談時</button>
                </div>
                <h2 class="compare-headline" id="c-headline">まずは電話0本。<br>相場だけ静かに確認。</h2>
                <div class="compare-subline" id="c-subline">個人情報なしでAI査定。営業電話の前に、愛車の価値だけを見られます。</div>

                <div class="zero-call">
                  <div class="burden-box">
